column2: "The welcome party was a great success, Leader. I'm so glad Akhtar and Khorshid enjoyed themselves."
"Getting together to eat and play in the water was so much fun! Thanks for helping us make it possible!"
"I'm grateful too. But next time, let me treat you to some of my home town's dishes."
"Now that I can taste what I'm making, I'll finally be able to do it justice! Just you wait and see!"

"That's right, you told us about your home town's food before...
Hehe, I'm looking forward to it!"
